## Installing dependencies

Let's install the missing dependency using the `composer` container:
```shell
docker run --rm \
    -v $(pwd):/opt \
    -w /opt \
    laravelsail/php80-composer:latest \
    bash -c "composer require --with-all-dependencies league/flysystem-aws-s3-v3:\"~1.0\""
```

